channel.title: RSMV .exe (corrects most running issues)
channel.description:
Alot of people get that Exception in thread "main" java.land.NoClassDefFoundError: Main
thing... well this .exe i wrote will correct that, just put it in your rsmv file and run this... it will extract all current models from runescape...
NOTE: it doesnt compile it.. u will need to do that yourself and last time i checkd rs was at version 546...
You dont need to download if u dont need.... but here is a screeny of it [img]http://i39.tinypic.com/34xhk41.png[/img]
if u get any other errors just tell me and ill see what i can do... I had to personally write this one cause i use a laptop and RSMV doesnt like to work on them for some reason... heres the DL link btw: [url=http://www.mediafire.com/download.php?nznvjjzjgzt]~click here~[/url] to download
PS: if this is wrong section please tell me correct one... i figured rsmv has to deal with models so i would post it here...[br][br][size=1]Posted on: May 20, 2009, 08:19:23 pm[/size][hr]wow im shocked that with the amount of people that cant run rsmv.. me making a new runner for it.. that nobody uses it
